snippet.title: Johnny Depp OFFICIALLY Sentenced To 2 Years In Prison - Amber Heard Wins...
snippet.description:

It's going to happen a mere few months before Johnny has to face off with his ex-wife in court. We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!

What do you think of the placement of it being so close to his other major court case? Will he be able to win this case as well as the other one?
